{"tid":2059631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲總理莫里森：不屈服於中國脅迫　不放棄澳洲自身價值","createTime":"2020-06-11T05:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T05:50:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d8bc28d0f0ceb0071d9591836b347f5f421d40bf","tid":2059631,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"澳洲總理莫里森強調，不會屈服於中國的脅迫，不放棄澳洲自身的價值。<br />\n<br />\n北京當局日前先後發出建議國民切勿前往澳洲旅遊的「安全提醒」，以及提醒留學生謹慎選擇前往澳洲學習的「留學預警」。莫里森接受當地電台訪問時，首次以「脅迫」形容中方的行動，表示雖然澳洲是一個開放貿易的國家，但他絕不會為應對來自任何地方的脅迫，而以澳洲的價值作交換，強調永遠只為國家利益行動，不會被威脅嚇倒。<br />\n<br />\n對於中方指新型肺炎疫情期間，澳洲發生多宗針對亞裔的歧視事件，變得不安全，莫里森拒絕接受有關說法，形容是荒謬、瞎說。被問到為何中國會提出有關關注，莫里森說，這是中國領導人的事，重申澳洲會提供世界上最好的旅遊及教育產品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531431-20200611.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531431-20200611.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjROIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=c27d4757\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531431-20200611.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2e7c6aba\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531431-20200611.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6e34d1126bce490d6a83d27a28beb518b5917405","tid":2059631,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:19:30.000Z","msg":"如果個個歐洲國家都咁硬<br />\n中國一早撤回國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2947952d4d5f0e355bdf1281da91797ccf152e00","tid":2059631,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:21:23.000Z","msg":"2020年頭山火俾人鬧到咁以為佢要落台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估唔到肺炎反cup後拉隊反埋共"},{"pid":"f9c5a30685056e1cc0f391e64b4f3bdd9ebb9ba2","tid":2059631,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:21:54.000Z","msg":"5 eyes<img src=\